Package: statConsultantAddin
Type: Package
Title: Stat Consultant RStudio Addin
Version: 0.1.0
Description: RStudio Addin for Stat Consultant. Polls the chat backend's
    pending-code queue and inserts received code at the cursor position of
    the active source document (rstudioapi::insertText). Zero-config auth via
    a local shared-secret file the backend generates. Environment sync is not
    yet implemented (Step 7).
License: Proprietary
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    rstudioapi,
    httr2,
    later
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
